# FR4: W-G-Q-G-T-L-V-T-V-S-S

################################
## VHH HALLMARK RESIDUES (IMGT positions)
################################
# Position 37 (FR2): VH typically V or F → VHH typically G or A
# Position 44 (FR2): VH typically G → VHH typically E
# Position 45 (FR2): VH typically L → VHH typically R
# Position 47 (FR2): VH typically W → VHH typically F, G, or L (critical for solubility)

